---

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4">
      Case Study FAQs
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Questions about our results and how we work
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Grid - Two Independent Columns (Desktop only) -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    
    <!-- Left Column -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-left w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq1"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Are these real case studies?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, absolutely. Every case study on this page is from an actual customer we've worked with. No made-up numbers. No hypothetical scenarios. These are real businesses with real results. We verify and track every metric we show you because we want you to see exactly what's possible when strategy meets execution.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-left w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq3"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Are results like these guaranteed?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">No. Each industry, market, and business is different. Market demand, competition, and business readiness all impact results. But here's what we can tell you: these results aren't uncommon. We've built a system that works across different industries because we focus on the fundamentals—strategic targeting, conversion optimization, and daily performance management. Your specific numbers might be different, but the methodology is proven.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-left w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq5"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">How long does it take to get results?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">We've seen meaningful results within a month. Some of our fastest wins came in just weeks. That said, most of our clients stay with us for years because they understand that sustainable growth compounds. The longer you work with us, the better we optimize your campaigns, the more we understand your market, and the stronger your results become. This is a partnership, not a quick fix.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-left w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq7"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Can you share client names or testimonials?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">Some clients are happy to go on record. Others prefer privacy—we respect that. During your consultation, we can connect you with references in your industry or market who've achieved similar results. We'd rather show you verified numbers and real impact than promise you celebrity endorsements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-right w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq2"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">What if my business is different?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">It probably is. Every business has unique challenges, markets, and opportunities. That's exactly why we start with discovery. We analyze your specific situation, market demand, competition, and business readiness to build a strategy customized for you. Our methodology is proven, but our execution is always tailored to your needs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-right w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq4"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">What industries have you worked in?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">We've worked across diverse industries—from home services and professional services to healthcare, medical spas, and more. You'll see that diversity in our case studies. The beauty of our system is that it works because it focuses on universal marketing fundamentals: finding the right audience, delivering the right message, and optimizing for conversion. The industry changes; the methodology doesn't.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-right w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq6"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">What if I've had bad experiences with other agencies?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">We hear this often, and honestly, it's what makes us different. Most agencies focus on volume and churn. We focus on results and retention. We take on fewer clients so we can obsess over each one. We track everything so you can see exactly what's happening with your money. And we optimize continuously instead of checking in monthly. If you've been burned before, we get it. Our case studies and client retention rates speak for themselves.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <button 
          class="faq-toggle-right w-full p-6 flex items-start gap-4 hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-left" 
          data-faq="case-faq8"
        >
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">How do I know this will work for me?</h3>
          </div>
          <svg 
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
            viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
            fill="none" 
            stroke="currentColor" 
            stroke-width="2" 
            class="faq-icon w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1 transition-transform duration-300"
          >
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-content hidden px-6 pb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-600">You schedule a consultation. We do a thorough analysis of your market, competition, and business. We'll tell you honestly whether we think we can help. If we can, we'll show you exactly what we recommend and what realistic results look like for your situation. No high-pressure sales pitch. Just strategy backed by data. If it's not a fit, we'll tell you that too.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  // Ensure all FAQs start hidden on page load
  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-content').forEach(content => {
      content.classList.add('hidden');
    });
  });

  // LEFT COLUMN - Independent accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle-left').forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const card = this.closest('.bg-white');
      const content = card.querySelector('.faq-content');
      const icon = this.querySelector('.faq-icon');
      
      // Close all OTHER FAQs in LEFT column only
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle-left').forEach(otherButton => {
        if (otherButton !== this) {
          const otherCard = otherButton.closest('.bg-white');
          const otherContent = otherCard.querySelector('.faq-content');
          const otherIcon = otherButton.querySelector('.faq-icon');
          otherContent.classList.add('hidden');
          otherIcon.classList.remove('rotate-180');
        }
      });
      
      // Toggle current FAQ
      content.classList.toggle('hidden');
      icon.classList.toggle('rotate-180');
    });
  });

  // RIGHT COLUMN - Independent accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle-right').forEach(button => {
    button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const card = this.closest('.bg-white');
      const content = card.querySelector('.faq-content');
      const icon = this.querySelector('.faq-icon');
      
      // Close all OTHER FAQs in RIGHT column only
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-toggle-right').forEach(otherButton => {
        if (otherButton !== this) {
          const otherCard = otherButton.closest('.bg-white');
          const otherContent = otherCard.querySelector('.faq-content');
          const otherIcon = otherButton.querySelector('.faq-icon');
          otherContent.classList.add('hidden');
          otherIcon.classList.remove('rotate-180');
        }
      });
      
      // Toggle current FAQ
      content.classList.toggle('hidden');
      icon.classList.toggle('rotate-180');
    });
  });
</script>